1
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:14,960
Your Highness.

2
00:00:15,670 --> 00:00:16,960
Have you persuaded

3
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:17,830
Prince Lie?

4
00:00:18,760 --> 00:00:19,280
Of course.

5
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:22,480
A bold young man like Changying
is bound to lose his heart

6
00:00:22,640 --> 00:00:25,000
when he meets a woman as extraordinary

7
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:26,320
as the Commandery Princess.

8
00:00:27,390 --> 00:00:29,830
I couldn't bear to see
someone born to be a great general

9
00:00:29,830 --> 00:00:30,912
trapped in the treacherous

10
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:33,070
and calculated world
of the imperial capital.

11
00:00:35,430 --> 00:00:36,240
What about you?

12
00:00:36,430 --> 00:00:37,000
Me?

13
00:00:38,240 --> 00:00:39,750
Someone as frail and sickly as I am

14
00:00:40,110 --> 00:00:41,960
is better suited
for matters of the heart.

15
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:51,790
Huayong.

16
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:52,830
Changying?

17
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:54,240
What are you doing here?

18
00:00:54,416 --> 00:00:55,840
I went to the East Palace earlier.

19
00:00:55,888 --> 00:00:58,020
The attendants said
you were in the Imperial Garden.

20
00:00:58,030 --> 00:00:59,150
So I came

21
00:00:59,350 --> 00:01:00,390
to thank you in person.

22
00:01:01,750 --> 00:01:02,560
We're brothers.

23
00:01:02,608 --> 00:01:04,016
There's no need for formalities.

24
00:01:04,310 --> 00:01:05,640
Your words

25
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:07,040
were a true awakening for me.

26
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:10,310
I've decided to ask for Commandery
Princess Zhaoning's hand in marriage.

27
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:12,150
Between the Anlan Army
and the Northwest Army,

28
00:01:12,150 --> 00:01:13,120
I can only choose one.

29
00:01:15,408 --> 00:01:17,300
I'm willing to give up
command of the Anlan Army

30
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,920
and serve under the Duke of Wei

31
00:01:19,310 --> 00:01:20,790
as one of the Northwest Army.

32
00:01:20,912 --> 00:01:22,896
This is my pledge
to the commandery princess.

33
00:01:22,944 --> 00:01:24,896
It will also fulfill my wish
to defend our homeland

34
00:01:24,944 --> 00:01:26,368
and fight on the battlefield.

35
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,560
I...

36
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,200
Is that

37
00:01:34,870 --> 00:01:36,230
what I meant?

38
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:38,760
Rest assured, Huayong.

39
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,950
I'll never tell Changqing
about your advice.

40
00:01:42,096 --> 00:01:43,510
At the hunting grounds that day,

41
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:46,256
you also confessed your feelings
to the Commandery Princess.

42
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,560
Yet you still put my happiness first.

43
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,510
I truly admire

44
00:01:50,576 --> 00:01:52,176
your generosity and character.

45
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,200
If one day

46
00:01:53,312 --> 00:01:54,920
I truly marry the Commandery Princess,

47
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:55,790
the first person

48
00:01:56,350 --> 00:01:57,280
I'll thank will be you.

49
00:01:58,880 --> 00:01:59,936
I'll take my leave.

50
00:02:06,350 --> 00:02:06,920
Your Highness.

51
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,800
So this is how you persuaded Prince Lie?

52
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:37,696
=Blossoms of Power=

53
00:03:37,700 --> 00:03:40,544
(Adapted from the novel, After My
Bloom, All Flowers Wither by Jin Huang)

54
00:03:40,580 --> 00:03:43,540
=Episode 8=

55
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:52,630
How lovely.

56
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,910
Come take a look.

57
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:58,430
Mother, come have something delicious.

58
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,910
It's the Double Ninth Festival.

59
00:04:00,910 --> 00:04:03,536
So many people have come to
Yunling Mountain to pray for blessings.

60
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:04,590
Your Highness.

61
00:04:04,624 --> 00:04:05,632
I prepared five color cakes

62
00:04:05,632 --> 00:04:07,712
and chrysanthemum liquor
early this morning.

63
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:10,240
Shall we find a place
to rest for a while?

64
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,080
All right.

65
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:13,360
Your Highness.

66
00:04:14,430 --> 00:04:15,840
The pavilion is full of young ladies.

67
00:04:16,016 --> 00:04:17,310
Please rest here for a while.

68
00:04:17,310 --> 00:04:18,680
I'll go buy you a kite.

69
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:24,950
Young Lady,

70
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:27,070
would you like a cornel bracelet?

71
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:29,270
There's only one left.

72
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:37,040
Thank you, Young Lady.

73
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,480
Let's rest up ahead.

74
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:06,950
All right.

75
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:07,920
Let's go.

76
00:05:08,830 --> 00:05:11,070
Such a sight is rarely seen.

77
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:11,720
Indeed.

78
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:23,310
- A snake!
- There is a snake!

79
00:05:36,896 --> 00:05:38,920
What's happening
on the mountaintop ahead?

80
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:39,720
Why is it so noisy?

81
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:41,190
Quick. Let's go take a look.

82
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:41,830
All right.

83
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,630
Your Highness.

84
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,120
Be careful not to get hurt.

85
00:06:11,136 --> 00:06:12,680
- Please forgive us, Your Highness.
- Please forgive us, Your Highness.

86
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,800
- We failed to protect you.
- We failed to protect you.

87
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:15,560
Get up.

88
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,750
This isn't your fault.

89
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,430
Your Highness!

90
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:20,240
I have failed you.

91
00:06:20,304 --> 00:06:21,750
I should never have left your side.

92
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:22,430
You too, get up.

93
00:06:23,472 --> 00:06:25,072
There's no need to blame yourself.

94
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,920
They were after me all along.

95
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:30,160
Who would use such a vicious method?

96
00:06:31,856 --> 00:06:33,584
We've already caught the culprit.

97
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:34,360
Move.

98
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:35,390
Let's go.

99
00:06:43,870 --> 00:06:46,480
Today, Tian Yuan and I came here
to pray for blessings.

100
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,310
When it happened,

101
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,040
we were halfway up the mountain.

102
00:06:50,390 --> 00:06:51,480
He must be the culprit.

103
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:53,270
Why are you arresting me?

104
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,750
You can't just seize people at random!

105
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:55,830
Is there no justice left?

106
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,240
The powerful are killing people!

107
00:06:57,310 --> 00:06:59,040
They treat human lives like nothing!

108
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:01,560
Everyone rushed toward the pavilion

109
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,800
to see what had happened.

110
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,000
Then why were you

111
00:07:04,032 --> 00:07:05,380
the only one heading the other way?

112
00:07:05,390 --> 00:07:06,920
I had an urgent matter at home.

113
00:07:06,976 --> 00:07:08,800
Was I not allowed
to hurry down the mountain?

114
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:11,190
You handled snakes
to keep from being bitten,

115
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:13,160
so you covered your hands with realgar.

116
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:15,040
Why would an ordinary hiker

117
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:17,190
coat both hands with realgar?

118
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,560
I've been bitten by snakes before.

119
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,630
I use realgar to keep them away.

120
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,160
What law have I broken?

121
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,160
Little girl, come here.

122
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:31,630
Tell me,

123
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,270
who told you

124
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,830
to sell me this cornel bracelet?

125
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:36,360
It was him.

126
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,560
You little brat!

127
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:40,240
How can you make up such lies?

128
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,630
You're talking nonsense!

129
00:07:43,310 --> 00:07:44,950
You sprinkled snake lure powder on it

130
00:07:45,430 --> 00:07:46,480
to attract venomous snakes.

131
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,160
The cornel

132
00:07:48,192 --> 00:07:49,856
masked the scent
of the snake lure powder.

133
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,632
The evidence and witnesses are all here.

134
00:07:51,808 --> 00:07:53,456
What else do you
have to say for yourself?

135
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:54,000
I...

136
00:07:55,792 --> 00:07:57,070
Still not telling the truth?

137
00:07:57,600 --> 00:08:00,390
It was the second young lady
of Vice Minister Hu's family.

138
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,950
I had no choice but to obey.

139
00:08:04,270 --> 00:08:05,480
(It's Hu Yingrao.)

140
00:08:11,950 --> 00:08:12,630
Tian Yuan.

141
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,600
Hand this man over to Cui Jinbai.

142
00:08:14,750 --> 00:08:16,390
He'll take care of the rest.

143
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,190
Yes.

144
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:20,680
Let's go.

145
00:08:27,584 --> 00:08:28,830
It's rare to come up here.

146
00:08:29,510 --> 00:08:30,750
Don't let that wretched girl

147
00:08:30,848 --> 00:08:32,320
from the Hu family spoil your mood.

148
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,360
Allow me to treat you to some tea.

149
00:08:35,670 --> 00:08:36,496
What do you say?

150
00:08:43,510 --> 00:08:45,550
Had Your Highness
not captured the culprit,

151
00:08:45,870 --> 00:08:47,000
he would've escaped by now.

152
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:49,150
Thank you, Your Highness.

153
00:08:49,968 --> 00:08:51,456
There's no need for thanks.

154
00:08:51,790 --> 00:08:52,670
Your business

155
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:53,910
is my business.

156
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:04,630
How do you intend

157
00:09:05,030 --> 00:09:06,440
to deal with Hu Yingrao?

158
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,670
Seat her

159
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,390
where I was sitting in the pavilion.

160
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,240
Release the venomous snakes.

161
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,750
Whether she's bitten

162
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:19,150
or falls off the cliff

163
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,000
will depend on her own fate.

164
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:25,630
You are as decisive as ever.

165
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:26,960
Truly bold and heroic.

166
00:09:32,910 --> 00:09:35,120
Do you think Hu Yingrao targeted you

167
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,960
simply because of your beauty?

168
00:09:41,664 --> 00:09:43,870
Hu Yingrao is a distant relative
of Noble Consort Rong.

169
00:09:43,904 --> 00:09:45,990
She has come and gone
from the palace since childhood.

170
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:48,120
Noble Consort Rong dotes on her greatly.

171
00:09:48,272 --> 00:09:50,576
She has always hoped to unite
the families through marriage.

172
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,510
She is the one Noble Consort Rong

173
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,150
truly wanted to become

174
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,360
Prince Lie's consort.

175
00:10:17,024 --> 00:10:18,096
Please enjoy your tea.

176
00:10:23,860 --> 00:10:26,340
(Duke of Wei's Manor)

177
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,910
There's some skin balm in here.

178
00:10:28,390 --> 00:10:29,480
It's highly effective

179
00:10:29,630 --> 00:10:30,550
for cuts and bruises.

180
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:33,630
My apologies, Prince Lie.

181
00:10:33,664 --> 00:10:35,310
The Commandery Princess
gave strict orders

182
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:37,030
that nothing may be accepted.

183
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:37,960
And...

184
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:39,910
she won't see you either.

185
00:10:43,030 --> 00:10:44,030
She means

186
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,750
to draw a clear line between us?

187
00:10:48,784 --> 00:10:51,360
The Commandery Princess
has never had feelings for you.

188
00:11:27,300 --> 00:11:32,300
(Duke of Wei's Manor)

189
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,000
Your Highness.

190
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:58,000
Prince Lie is still standing
outside the gate.

191
00:11:58,360 --> 00:12:00,390
At this rate,
he'll stand there all night.

192
00:12:00,448 --> 00:12:01,750
The rain is coming down so hard.

193
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:03,270
Won't he get sick?

194
00:12:04,390 --> 00:12:05,440
Go tell him

195
00:12:05,632 --> 00:12:07,536
he's free to stand
in the rain wherever he likes.

196
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:10,000
Just not in front
of Duke of Wei's Manor.

197
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,150
Your Highness.

198
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:14,440
Prince Lie is deeply devoted to you.

199
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:16,030
Don't you think

200
00:12:16,390 --> 00:12:17,840
you're being too harsh?

201
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,270
One moment you show concern,

202
00:12:19,328 --> 00:12:20,512
the next you soften your heart.

203
00:12:20,630 --> 00:12:22,440
How long can this back and forth go on?

204
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:26,000
Indecision only brings more trouble.

205
00:12:28,790 --> 00:12:29,390
Yes.

206
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,200
Your Highness.

207
00:12:35,390 --> 00:12:38,000
Will you still meet
the Crown Prince tomorrow?

208
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,150
Yes.

209
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:42,550
The Crown Prince is rather strange.

210
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:44,790
Your Highness, your injuries
delayed you for several days.

211
00:12:44,870 --> 00:12:46,670
The Double Ninth Festival
has already ended.

212
00:12:46,752 --> 00:12:48,600
Why does he still
want you to go up the tower?

213
00:12:49,232 --> 00:12:51,510
I gave him my word
that I'd accompany him up the tower.

214
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,360
I intend to keep it.

215
00:13:00,100 --> 00:13:02,460
(Favorable Weather
and Abundant Harvests)

216
00:13:02,870 --> 00:13:03,550
Your Highness.

217
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,480
The Double Ninth Festival is over.

218
00:13:06,032 --> 00:13:07,720
The lantern market
has already been cleared.

219
00:13:08,670 --> 00:13:11,000
You invited me up here
to admire the lanterns.

220
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:13,080
Which lanterns did you wish to show me?

221
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:38,840
Do you like it,

222
00:13:40,270 --> 00:13:41,200
even just a little?

223
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:44,910
Fireworks are beautiful,

224
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:46,750
but they fade in an instant,

225
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:48,840
leaving only lingering regret.

226
00:14:22,560 --> 00:14:25,210
♪The timeless wind and moon♪

227
00:14:25,790 --> 00:14:29,400
♪Quietly reflect in your sparkling eyes♪

228
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,256
Commandery Princess.

229
00:14:30,368 --> 00:14:32,000
Every lantern across the city tonight

230
00:14:32,032 --> 00:14:33,720
was specially made
at Crown Prince's command

231
00:14:33,792 --> 00:14:35,030
and delivered to every household.

232
00:14:35,792 --> 00:14:38,224
The palace invited eminent monks
to offer prayers and blessings.

233
00:14:38,288 --> 00:14:40,360
Any household that keeps
its lanterns lit until dawn

234
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:41,960
will receive the monks' blessings.

235
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:43,480
That's why

236
00:14:43,520 --> 00:14:45,000
the people have all joined in eagerly.

237
00:14:45,790 --> 00:14:47,030
It's even grander than

238
00:14:47,390 --> 00:14:48,870
the Double Ninth Lantern Festival.

239
00:14:49,770 --> 00:14:53,570
♪Not a trace of sorrow can be found♪

240
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,080
I can feel

241
00:15:06,064 --> 00:15:07,696
the thought you put into all this.

242
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:12,440
I simply took the opportunity

243
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,440
to bring you

244
00:15:15,150 --> 00:15:16,120
a little joy.

245
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:24,960
Thank you

246
00:15:25,024 --> 00:15:27,380
for letting me behold
the splendor of the imperial capital.

247
00:15:27,390 --> 00:15:28,440
The wind is strong up here.

248
00:15:28,640 --> 00:15:30,336
You shouldn't stay out
and catch a chill.

249
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:32,150
We should head back.

250
00:15:35,910 --> 00:15:36,480
All right.

251
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:39,504
I'll walk you back.

252
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:49,510
By the way,

253
00:15:51,270 --> 00:15:52,200
how are your injuries?

254
00:15:54,880 --> 00:15:56,848
I had that ointment
prepared especially for you.

255
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:00,600
Thank you for your kindness.

256
00:16:02,832 --> 00:16:04,736
With such
a beautiful display of lanterns,

257
00:16:05,150 --> 00:16:06,550
I'd like to stroll a little longer.

258
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:07,550
All right.

259
00:16:25,392 --> 00:16:27,104
There's something I'd like to tell you.

260
00:16:29,504 --> 00:16:31,072
What happened with the Hu family

261
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:32,352
was my fault for involving you.

262
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:35,240
I came to apologize.

263
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:37,790
It's already over.

264
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:39,200
I'm unharmed.

265
00:16:39,216 --> 00:16:40,720
Please don't worry, Prince Lie.

266
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:46,848
Commandery Princess.

267
00:16:48,576 --> 00:16:50,336
What is it about me
that isn't good enough?

268
00:16:50,400 --> 00:16:52,112
Everyone has their own preference.

269
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:54,120
Just because you have feelings for me,

270
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,720
does that mean I have to be grateful?

271
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:58,120
That's not what I meant.

272
00:16:58,270 --> 00:16:59,600
I've told you before.

273
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:01,600
Don't set your heart on me.

274
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:08,750
I've already given my heart away!

275
00:17:09,070 --> 00:17:10,310
I can never take it back!

276
00:17:11,590 --> 00:17:13,790
That's just how life is.

277
00:17:13,856 --> 00:17:15,630
There will always be
things beyond our reach.

278
00:17:15,648 --> 00:17:16,896
I hope you will soon let go.

279
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:29,830
Changqing.

280
00:17:33,310 --> 00:17:33,920
Changying.

281
00:17:35,550 --> 00:17:36,310
Let's go.

282
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,830
A young lady like her

283
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,240
can't be won over

284
00:17:44,510 --> 00:17:45,640
by persistence.

285
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:48,070
But...

286
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:50,590
The more you cling to her,

287
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,440
the more determined she'll be

288
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:54,750
to leave you.

289
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:10,030
Have we come a little too far?

290
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:12,880
Then please rest here for a moment.

291
00:18:13,030 --> 00:18:14,310
I'll go bring the carriage over.

292
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:14,920
All right.

293
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:43,920
Your Highness!

294
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:45,790
Your Highness!

295
00:19:04,928 --> 00:19:07,030
Noble Consort Rong
may look kind, but she's ruthless.

296
00:19:07,110 --> 00:19:08,110
Her methods are vicious.

297
00:19:08,310 --> 00:19:09,440
Anyone who knows the truth

298
00:19:09,584 --> 00:19:11,312
would never want
to marry into that family

299
00:19:11,510 --> 00:19:12,830
and serve a mother-in-law like her.

300
00:19:14,790 --> 00:19:16,750
Still, both Changqing and Changying

301
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:19,070
are unwaveringly devoted,

302
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:20,110
each deeply in love.

303
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:22,830
Your Highness.

304
00:19:22,840 --> 00:19:24,270
You must come up with a plan quickly.

305
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:25,030
Otherwise,

306
00:19:25,104 --> 00:19:26,550
if you don't root out the problem,

307
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:28,110
it will only return.

308
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:33,000
How have we walked this far

309
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,240
without seeing Zhaoning?

310
00:20:32,480 --> 00:20:33,110
Speak.

311
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,400
Who sent you?

312
00:20:39,536 --> 00:20:41,968
Your Highness, he bit down
on poison and killed himself.

313
00:20:46,590 --> 00:20:47,240
Xihe.

314
00:20:50,352 --> 00:20:51,540
Tian Yuan, prepare the horses.

315
00:20:51,550 --> 00:20:51,960
Yes.

316
00:21:02,496 --> 00:21:04,580
The Commandery Princess's
pulse is extremely unstable.

317
00:21:04,590 --> 00:21:05,504
I've used acupuncture

318
00:21:05,568 --> 00:21:07,616
to temporarily stabilize
her heart meridian.

319
00:21:08,270 --> 00:21:09,830
But even if she wakes tomorrow,

320
00:21:10,144 --> 00:21:11,968
if she doesn't receive better treatment,

321
00:21:12,510 --> 00:21:15,880
I'm afraid she'll spend the rest
of her life confined to this sickbed.

322
00:21:28,070 --> 00:21:29,480
Just tell the Commandery Princess

323
00:21:31,030 --> 00:21:32,400
that she needs complete rest.

324
00:21:33,168 --> 00:21:34,768
Don't tell her anything else for now.

325
00:21:35,510 --> 00:21:36,000
Yes.

326
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:44,030
Your Highness.

327
00:21:44,350 --> 00:21:45,270
I found

328
00:21:45,440 --> 00:21:46,790
traces of liquor in the body.

329
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:48,880
The assassin drank Jieqianchou.

330
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:55,310
Jieqianchou is an imperial liquor.

331
00:21:55,488 --> 00:21:56,960
It's only available in the palace.

332
00:21:57,024 --> 00:21:58,440
A fixed amount is issued every year,

333
00:21:58,750 --> 00:22:00,110
and every bottle is accounted for.

334
00:22:00,750 --> 00:22:01,880
We only need to find out

335
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:04,240
who gave him the Jieqianchou,

336
00:22:04,550 --> 00:22:05,510
and we'll know

337
00:22:05,790 --> 00:22:06,720
who

338
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:08,830
tried to harm Zhaoning.

339
00:22:09,830 --> 00:22:11,110
I'll investigate it at once.

340
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:17,568
Still no word from Hua Fuhai
about the Extreme Frost Cordyceps?

341
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:18,720
Only that medicine

342
00:22:18,816 --> 00:22:20,912
can stabilize
Commandery Princess's heart meridian.

343
00:22:20,960 --> 00:22:22,480
I've already sent people to inquire.

344
00:22:22,832 --> 00:22:24,176
It grows on the highest peaks

345
00:22:24,440 --> 00:22:25,590
of the frozen wilderness.

346
00:22:26,336 --> 00:22:28,480
The experts we've sent
have risked their lives,

347
00:22:29,024 --> 00:22:30,592
yet still haven't found it.

348
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:58,480
Physician Xie.

349
00:22:59,590 --> 00:23:00,720
Why are her hands so cold?

350
00:23:21,590 --> 00:23:22,270
You're awake.

351
00:23:23,830 --> 00:23:25,030
It's you.

352
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:30,310
Come.

353
00:23:33,872 --> 00:23:35,248
What do you mean, "it's you"?

354
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:37,270
I thought

355
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:40,000
the one who saved me

356
00:23:41,270 --> 00:23:42,110
was you.

357
00:23:52,790 --> 00:23:53,920
I wish it had been.

358
00:23:55,590 --> 00:23:56,680
But the one who saved you

359
00:23:57,400 --> 00:23:58,480
was my guard.

360
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:06,750
Still, hearing you say that

361
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:08,200
makes me very happy.

362
00:24:13,904 --> 00:24:14,920
Commandery Princess.

363
00:24:16,256 --> 00:24:18,704
I have urgent business
that requires me to leave the capital.

364
00:24:19,070 --> 00:24:20,160
Take good care of yourself.

365
00:24:20,510 --> 00:24:22,160
I'll come see you again in a few days.

366
00:24:26,790 --> 00:24:27,880
Take care.

367
00:24:43,270 --> 00:24:44,590
Do you know

368
00:24:46,440 --> 00:24:48,070
how much I wished you'd ask me

369
00:24:50,310 --> 00:24:51,440
where I was going

370
00:24:53,030 --> 00:24:54,070
and what I was going to do?

371
00:24:55,160 --> 00:24:56,590
I'm sure you have your reasons.

372
00:24:57,550 --> 00:24:58,720
There's no need for me to ask.

373
00:25:08,512 --> 00:25:09,536
Your Highness,

374
00:25:10,110 --> 00:25:11,440
are you truly going in person?

375
00:25:11,856 --> 00:25:14,000
The extreme cold will worsen
the poison inside your body.

376
00:25:14,070 --> 00:25:15,110
The danger will be immense.

377
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:29,680
Zhaoning.

378
00:25:31,270 --> 00:25:32,830
How I wish that one day

379
00:25:34,750 --> 00:25:36,240
you would be reluctant

380
00:25:37,830 --> 00:25:38,920
to see me leave.

381
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:48,400
♪Let it all go♪

382
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:51,040
♪Give my tears to the flowers♪

383
00:26:52,650 --> 00:26:55,340
♪Beneath my feet, eternal doom♪

384
00:26:55,340 --> 00:26:58,410
♪Is more than wind and sand♪

385
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:05,090
♪That perfectly plotted love
hides in the clamor♪

386
00:27:06,740 --> 00:27:12,110
♪Between us,
it's both treacherous and flawless♪

387
00:27:12,128 --> 00:27:13,168
Before Crown Prince left,

388
00:27:13,216 --> 00:27:14,480
he said that at this time of year,

389
00:27:14,480 --> 00:27:16,710
the foreign kingdoms
would present pomegranates as tribute.

390
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:17,648
They're juicy and sweet.

391
00:27:17,690 --> 00:27:20,230
Their juice can be used to
make pastries for Commandery Princess.

392
00:27:20,240 --> 00:27:21,380
They're especially delicious.

393
00:27:21,904 --> 00:27:23,536
Please thank the Crown Prince for me.

394
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:25,504
While Commandery Princess
recovers in bed,

395
00:27:25,552 --> 00:27:27,350
seeing these bright red pomegranates

396
00:27:27,480 --> 00:27:28,510
may lift her spirits.

397
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:30,310
When will the Crown Prince return?

398
00:27:31,030 --> 00:27:32,720
♪My heart rises and falls♪

399
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:34,000
There's no news yet.

400
00:27:34,560 --> 00:27:36,000
♪In this eternity♪

401
00:27:36,030 --> 00:27:37,968
Why did the Crown Prince
leave the capital?

402
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:39,880
What was it for...

403
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:40,992
I'm not quite sure either.

404
00:27:41,040 --> 00:27:43,072
If there's nothing else,
I'll take my leave.

405
00:27:43,210 --> 00:27:44,960
♪Sober, it's all like a dream♪

406
00:27:44,960 --> 00:27:48,510
♪Stars sink into my hair,
the moon slips through my fingers♪

407
00:27:48,510 --> 00:27:51,920
♪For how much joy
do we share this life together♪

408
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:55,440
♪Withering and flourishing,
year after year♪

409
00:28:14,080 --> 00:28:14,790
Your Highness...

410
00:28:15,510 --> 00:28:18,300
♪Spring brings life,
autumn brings death♪

411
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:25,720
♪A heart weathered
by frost will melt in love♪

412
00:28:26,670 --> 00:28:28,620
♪Across countless miles
of treasured moments♪

413
00:28:28,620 --> 00:28:32,490
♪Every move is a game of truth and lies♪

414
00:28:35,024 --> 00:28:36,000
Commandery Princess...

415
00:28:36,460 --> 00:28:39,420
♪I'll become your armor♪

416
00:28:40,160 --> 00:28:41,184
I'll take my leave.

417
00:28:41,232 --> 00:28:46,370
♪I want destiny,
and also tender words of love♪

418
00:28:46,560 --> 00:28:54,190
♪As night stains my eyes,
I'll gaze once more at the rosy clouds♪

419
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:58,180
♪I have a dream
of a long wind in my sleeves♪

420
00:28:58,180 --> 00:29:01,770
♪My heart rises and falls,
we embrace in a sea of clouds♪

421
00:29:01,770 --> 00:29:05,290
♪In this eternity, you are a part of it♪

422
00:29:05,290 --> 00:29:08,760
♪My longing can level mountains
and cross countless rivers♪

423
00:29:08,760 --> 00:29:12,260
♪Drunk or sober, it's all like a dream♪

424
00:29:12,260 --> 00:29:15,720
♪Stars sink into my hair,
the moon slips through my fingers♪

425
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:19,160
♪For how much joy
do we share this life together♪

426
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:22,520
♪Withering and flourishing,
year after year♪

427
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,200
Your Highness!

428
00:29:58,750 --> 00:29:59,550
Your Highness!

429
00:29:59,920 --> 00:30:00,720
Your Highness!

430
00:30:09,072 --> 00:30:10,832
Deliver this
to the Commandery Princess...

431
00:30:11,310 --> 00:30:12,440
There must be no mistake...

432
00:30:13,160 --> 00:30:13,590
Yes.

433
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:23,480
Hurry! Faster!

434
00:30:32,510 --> 00:30:33,270
Your Highness.

435
00:30:33,480 --> 00:30:35,440
This Extreme Frost Cordyceps
is incredibly rare.

436
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:36,680
Just its fragrance alone

437
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:38,000
is enough to refresh the spirit.

438
00:30:48,640 --> 00:30:50,720
It was sent again by Hua Fuhai?

439
00:30:52,030 --> 00:30:53,720
What is the Tagara Incense

440
00:30:54,510 --> 00:30:55,510
behind him really after?

441
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:58,350
Your Highness,
this medicine is hard to come by.

442
00:30:59,070 --> 00:31:00,830
Your health must come first.

443
00:31:01,550 --> 00:31:02,030
Here.

444
00:31:09,328 --> 00:31:11,488
How is the investigation
into the assassin going?

445
00:31:12,350 --> 00:31:13,880
Following the Crown Prince's orders,

446
00:31:14,070 --> 00:31:16,000
I found the records on
where the Jieqianchou went.

447
00:31:16,550 --> 00:31:17,920
According to Physician Xie,

448
00:31:18,110 --> 00:31:19,550
the assassin didn't drink it that day.

449
00:31:19,550 --> 00:31:21,110
He drank it the day before,

450
00:31:21,240 --> 00:31:22,480
and at least 250 g.

451
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:23,400
250 g?

452
00:31:27,088 --> 00:31:28,920
Drinking before carrying out
the assassination

453
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:30,510
to steady his nerves is understandable.

454
00:31:31,750 --> 00:31:33,200
But 250 g...

455
00:31:33,210 --> 00:31:35,150
Wouldn't he be afraid
it would affect the mission?

456
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,544
Based on the condition of the body,

457
00:31:36,544 --> 00:31:38,950
Physician Xie concluded the assassin
was likely from the south.

458
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:40,440
I also asked Young Master Bu for help.

459
00:31:40,550 --> 00:31:43,296
But none of the southerners living in
or staying in the imperial capital

460
00:31:43,328 --> 00:31:44,170
are under suspicion.

461
00:31:44,270 --> 00:31:46,030
Drinking heavily
before the assassination,

462
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:48,200
then taking poison
the moment he was exposed,

463
00:31:48,510 --> 00:31:50,110
shows he was prepared to die.

464
00:31:51,350 --> 00:31:52,920
Perhaps that flask of Jieqianchou

465
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:53,960
was his reward.

466
00:31:54,310 --> 00:31:55,880
A final taste before dying.

467
00:31:56,790 --> 00:31:57,400
Mo Yu.

468
00:31:58,440 --> 00:31:59,510
Go find Young Master Bu,

469
00:32:00,070 --> 00:32:02,070
and ask him
to bring Vice Minister Cui here.

470
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:03,480
Yes.

471
00:32:10,030 --> 00:32:10,680
Young Master.

472
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:12,110
- What's wrong?
- Young Master.

473
00:32:12,110 --> 00:32:13,400
- You're ruining my plans.
- You really can't go in.

474
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:14,200
The Lord isn't here.

475
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:14,750
Jinbai.

476
00:32:15,350 --> 00:32:16,110
Feeling shy?

477
00:32:20,750 --> 00:32:21,510
Let him in.

478
00:32:25,312 --> 00:32:27,160
Vice Minister Cui
is upright and honorable,

479
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,672
yet this playboy keeps pestering him

480
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:30,160
and ruining his reputation everywhere.

481
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:30,920
Outrageous.

482
00:32:31,400 --> 00:32:32,200
Speak.

483
00:32:38,110 --> 00:32:39,510
Can't I come

484
00:32:40,550 --> 00:32:42,000
to see you?

485
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:50,590
A little flirting is harmless.

486
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:52,110
But drawing a blade

487
00:32:53,590 --> 00:32:54,750
hurts our friendship.

488
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:06,590
Wait.

489
00:33:14,880 --> 00:33:15,590
Shameless...

490
00:33:22,440 --> 00:33:23,110
Young Master.

491
00:33:23,110 --> 00:33:24,110
(The Greatest Form Is Formless)
You can't do this.

492
00:33:24,110 --> 00:33:25,720
- Where are you going?
- What's going on?

493
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:26,416
Out of the way.

494
00:33:44,510 --> 00:33:45,472
Go get a wet cloth,

495
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:47,480
and bring an incense sachet
to help revive him.

496
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:48,160
Yes.

497
00:34:06,110 --> 00:34:06,790
You're awake?

498
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:08,000
Want some?

499
00:34:08,320 --> 00:34:08,710
You...

500
00:34:08,960 --> 00:34:10,000
Mind yourself.

501
00:34:10,784 --> 00:34:12,544
Please don't take offense,
Your Highness.

502
00:34:16,670 --> 00:34:17,480
Your Highness.

503
00:34:17,792 --> 00:34:19,400
I was the one who invited you here.

504
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:20,920
If I've been disrespectful,

505
00:34:21,230 --> 00:34:22,630
please forgive me.

506
00:34:24,640 --> 00:34:26,190
How may I assist you, Your Highness?

507
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:27,520
I suspect someone

508
00:34:27,568 --> 00:34:29,320
was a death row inmate
who was switched out

509
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:30,670
from the imperial prison.

510
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:33,400
I'd like to ask you to investigate.

511
00:34:41,880 --> 00:34:44,190
Vice Minister Cui works remarkably fast.

512
00:34:46,110 --> 00:34:47,440
Aren't you on duty today?

513
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:49,440
You neglect your duties all day long.

514
00:34:49,472 --> 00:34:51,536
Aren't you afraid
the Grand Censor will impeach you?

515
00:34:52,590 --> 00:34:53,590
Grand Censor Tao knows

516
00:34:53,590 --> 00:34:55,552
the Commandery Princess and I
are close friends.

517
00:34:55,560 --> 00:34:56,760
He'd never impeach me.

518
00:35:02,190 --> 00:35:02,800
Your Highness.

519
00:35:03,210 --> 00:35:04,260
I've thoroughly investigated

520
00:35:04,270 --> 00:35:06,170
every government office
in the imperial capital.

521
00:35:06,208 --> 00:35:07,808
I did find the man you were looking for.

522
00:35:08,110 --> 00:35:09,590
The condemned man was named Zhang Zhuo.

523
00:35:09,632 --> 00:35:10,840
The one who bought his life

524
00:35:11,070 --> 00:35:12,920
was a poor scholar named Fu Jin.

525
00:35:12,944 --> 00:35:14,208
He's from Xianning Commandery.

526
00:35:16,030 --> 00:35:17,280
A poor scholar?

527
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:19,880
Why would he try to kill me?

528
00:35:22,070 --> 00:35:23,030
Was he

529
00:35:23,030 --> 00:35:24,760
close to any powerful officials?

530
00:35:25,590 --> 00:35:26,800
He kept to himself.

531
00:35:26,864 --> 00:35:27,792
His neighbors also said

532
00:35:27,800 --> 00:35:29,660
they never saw any wealthy
or influential people

533
00:35:29,670 --> 00:35:30,512
visiting his home.

534
00:35:32,630 --> 00:35:33,920
Xianning Commandery...

535
00:35:38,510 --> 00:35:39,630
If I remember correctly,

536
00:35:40,230 --> 00:35:41,590
the Bian family's ancestral home

537
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:42,590
was Xianning.

538
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:44,320
The Bian family?

539
00:35:44,510 --> 00:35:45,960
Isn't Bian Xianyi the only one left?

540
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:47,670
She has a grudge against you?

541
00:35:49,150 --> 00:35:50,510
I'm only making a guess.

542
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:52,230
An ancestral home alone

543
00:35:52,480 --> 00:35:53,280
proves nothing.

544
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:54,840
Why waste time thinking about it?

545
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:55,710
I'll have her arrested

546
00:35:55,808 --> 00:35:57,070
and beaten until she talks...

547
00:36:02,510 --> 00:36:03,360
Then

548
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:07,030
arrest Fu Jin?

549
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,360
I have plenty of ways

550
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:11,670
to deal with
a delicate young scholar like him.

551
00:36:13,280 --> 00:36:14,000
Young Master Bu.

552
00:36:15,190 --> 00:36:16,320
This is the imperial capital.

553
00:36:16,592 --> 00:36:18,560
You may disregard propriety
and indulge yourself,

554
00:36:18,624 --> 00:36:21,376
but you must never behave so frivolously
before the Commandery Princess.

555
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:24,190
Forget it.

556
